T02TD1775E:269b-1: shr'i ma h'a k'a la sto tra /
T02TD1775E:269b-3: dpal nag po chen po la bstod pa //
T02TD1775E:269b-4: dpal nag po chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1775E:269b-5: bcom ldan dpal chen grags pa yi //
T02TD1775E:269b-6: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa yis //
T02TD1775E:269b-7: nyid kyi thugs ka nas byung ste //
T02TD1775E:269b-9: h'um gi de nyid las bzhengs pa'i //
T02TD1775E:269b-10: zhal gcig phyag ni gnyis pa ste //
T02TD1775E:270a-2: bstan pa srung la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1775E:270a-3: thod pa rnam gsum 'bar ba yi //
T02TD1775E:270a-4: gzhal yas gur gyi nang na bzhugs //
T02TD1775E:270a-5: g-yas bskum g-yon brkyang bdud rnams mnan //
T02TD1775E:270a-7: ma chags thabs kyi padma mdzes //
T02TD1775E:270a-8: shes rab ye shes nyi ma'i dkyil //
T02TD1775E:270a-9: h'um las skyes pa'i dpa' bo ni //
T02TD1775E:270a-10: bstan pa bsrungs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1775E:270a-11: g-yas kyi gri gug gdengs pa yis //
T02TD1775E:270a-12: dgra bgegs 'dul zhing bdud mgo gcod //
T02TD1775E:270a-13: nyon mongs dug gsum rtsad nas 'joms //
T02TD1775E:270a-14: dpa' bo khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1775E:270a-15: bdud kyi thod pa bdud rtsis bkang //
T02TD1775E:270a-16: nyid kyi zhal du gsol bar mdzad //
T02TD1775E:270a-17: sgrub pa po la dngos grub stsol //
T02TD1775E:270a-19: zhal nas khrag gi rgyun 'dzag pa //
T02TD1775E:270a-20: bstan pa la gnod dal yams 'bebs //
T02TD1775E:270a-21: dam tshig bsrungs la dngos grub stsol //
T02TD1775E:270a-22: thugs rje che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1775E:270a-23: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
T02TD1775E:270a-24: mgo bo'i phreng bas do shal byas //
T02TD1775E:270a-25: dug lnga rtsad nas gcod pa ste //
T02TD1775E:270a-27: mche ba gtsigs pas bstan pa la //
T02TD1775E:270a-28: gnod pa'i klad pa 'joms par mdzad //
T02TD1775E:270a-29: til tsam dag tu brlag par mdzad //
T02TD1775E:270a-31: gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa'i //
T02TD1775E:270a-32: rkang med 'gro bas sku la brgyan //
T02TD1775E:270a-33: zhe sngang rtsad nas gcod pa ste //
T02TD1775E:270a-35: stag ni dpa' brjid rngam pa'i chas //
T02TD1775E:270a-36: sham thabs rked la bcings pa yis //
T02TD1775E:270a-37: dregs pa lha chen zil gyis gnon /
T02TD1775E:270a-39: bskal pa med dpung 'bar ba yi //
T02TD1775E:270a-40: srid pa'i rtse mor rab tu 'bar /
T02TD1775E:270a-41: bstan pa la gnod sgrol mdzad pa //
T02TD1775E:270a-42: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khyod la bstod //
T02TD1775E:270a-43: da bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
T02TD1775E:270a-44: tha ma'i bstan pa srung mdzad pa //
T02TD1775E:270a-45: thad pa lnga yis dbu la brgyan //
T02TD1775E:270a-47: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'khyil //
T02TD1775E:270a-48: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa yis //
T02TD1775E:270a-49: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rtags//
T02TD1775E:270b-0: @270b rtags lnga ldan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1775E:270b-1: spyan gsum du ga gsum rtsad nas 'joms //
T02TD1775E:270b-2: 'dul ba rnam pa bzhi gzigs nas //
T02TD1775E:270b-3: gang la ci 'dul ji bzhin du //
T02TD1775E:270b-5: dpal nag po chen po la bstod pa slob dpon chen po aa wa dh'u t'i pas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
